reviewText: Absolutely fantastic. I would recommend this for anyone interested in anything dealing with relationships and how God just might have some direction for us.
it s a must for allof us who are single!
Wonderful scripture backed wisdom on how to become the person God wants you to be and then find the right person !
This is a great series for both young and old though I wish I had heard it when I was young. I have watched many times on my own and with my teenagers and appreciate nuggets of wisdom it offers.
This is an eye opening, greatly needed teaching that I wish I had the privilege of listening to 20 years ago.
